Sarkozy Says Work ‘Advancing Well’ on Banks, EFSF

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-10-23T14:57:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/sarkozy-says-work-advancing-well-on-banks-efsf.html
President  Nicolas Sarkozy  said
European governments’ talks on bank capitalization and how to
increase the firepower of the European Financial Stability
Facility is “advancing well.” He spoke at a press conference
in Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
